{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9b777c7dca","title":"关于庐山会议简报上应一律称同志问题给刘少奇等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0ad383d5bb","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":3,"articleId":"9b777c7dca","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭真","id":"5fd56865b0","type":"人物"},{"name":"贺龙","id":"d0a2337495","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"63035f3550","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1959年7月2日至8月16日在庐山先后举行的中共中央政治局扩大会议和八届八中全会。"},{"id":"a918cdd706","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"fa63be1711","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时庐山会议所分各组的组长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"14e6dc2a2b","type":"title","text":"关于庐山会议“简报上应一律称同志问题给刘少奇等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63035f3550","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、恩来、彭真、尚昆同志，各组组长同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a918cdd706","type":"paragraph","text":"简报上对于同志的称呼不妥当，这种旧习惯应当改过来。建议：一律称某某同志。例如：主席，称毛泽东同志；总理，称周恩来同志；林总，彭总，贺总，称林彪同志，彭德怀同志，贺龙同志。其他，以此类推。如同意，请各组长在会上宣布一下。请尚昆告简报编者，一律从西日起照此改正","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa63be1711","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76270c2e90","type":"paragraph","text":"八月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9b777c7dca","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":254,"end":254}}}},"__N_SSG":true}